<https://w3id.org/gno#commitNoEffectiveChangesetHandling> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Defines how the commit operation should handle the case that no effective changes result from the changeset. The value MUST be one of the following: 'skip', 'proceed' or 'error'." .
